    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and represents the pinnacle of its model year. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster with absolutely no scratches or dings, and the interior is immaculate, showing no signs of wear on the premium upholstery. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs silently, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously maintained, top-tier vehicle that looks and drives like new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
