    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as expected, making it a reliable choice for daily commuting or longer trips. While it shows some minor signs of wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are functioning properly. Buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road without any immediate repair needs.",
