    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is looking for a new home where it can get the attention it deserves. While it's currently in poor condition and will need significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it represents a fantastic opportunity to build a car exactly how you want it! If you enjoy a rewarding challenge and bringing a classic back to its former glory, this is the perfect canvas for your next big project.",
